snippet.title: Costume Quest 2 | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Double Fine Productions and Midnight City are teaming up to bring you Costume Quest 2! More costumes, more quests and more candy than every before! 

Check out our websites:
http://www.midnight-city.com
http://www.doublefine.com

Follow us on twitter:
@Midnight_City - http://twitter.com/Midnight_City
@DoubleFine - http://twitter.com/DoubleFine

And on facebook:
Midnight City - http://facebook.com/midnightcitygames
Double Fine Productions - http://facebook.com/doublefineproductions
